title: GEORGE FLOYD ANNIVERSARY: Reflecting on the Summer of Love!
description: It’s the one-year anniversary of George Floyd’s death. We look back on the summer of love and/or violent fiery riots. Seth Rogen doesn’t understand comedy. Joe Biden doesn’t understand words. Elliot Page goes topless. And did you ever notice Democrats love crime because they hate America?
